            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%9120%E5%B9%B4%E6%9D%A5%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%82%BA%E7%99%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%9120%E5%B9%B4%E6%9D%A5%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%82%BA%E7%99%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#近20年来我国肺癌死亡人数持续上升#</span></a>】在我国，近20年来，肺癌发病与死亡人数一直呈上升趋势。肺癌早期没有明显症状，一旦出现咳痰带血、胸闷气短、声音嘶哑等症状就意味着病情比较晚了。有家族史、吸烟史、职业暴露等肺癌高危人群应定期进行低剂量螺旋CT筛查。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E6%97%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#今天是世界癌症日#</span></a>，一起了解👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4865358671314947" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1har7u6nfxwj60zk0k078d02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/M1G9G2b6lx082SzGohCo01041200p5Yi0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675659993&amp;ssig=Dh3C9eA8ug&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/QiLn36Selx082SzEvk4001041200bGJK0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675659993&amp;ssig=Ii9WRqIe0b&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/nk38mIsplx082SzEAlBK010412007hWO0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675659993&amp;ssig=68Uf%2BeEX4i&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://